{"type":"message","id":"158c08c9","parentId":"52755886","timestamp":"2026-04-07T06:15:09.225Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Current time: 14:15 (Asia/Shanghai) - this is within the afternoon work hours (13:30-18:00). I should check the heartbeat rules.\n\nThe heartbeat rules say:\n- 工作日 13:30-18:00 — 下午工作时段\n- 喝水提醒（10:30 / 14:30 / 16:30 附近）\n- 久坐提醒（连续工作超过 2 小时的时间点）\n\n14:15 is near the 14:30 water reminder time. I should remind about water. It's been more than 2 hours since last check (around 10:30-11:00). I should remind to drink water."},{"type":"text","text":"💧 14:30 了，喝口水活动一下！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775542501426}}
{"type":"message","id":"4ca2ccd8","parentId":"158c08c9","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:05:29.916Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b527e85449094c35219a29552545\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-07 15:05 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b527e85449094c35219a29552545]\nou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b: # WebProbe 服务研究笔记\n\n> 整理时间：2026-04-07\n\n## 概览\n\nWebProbe 是一个部署在 K8s 内网的网页抓取服务，供 OpenClaw 的 `webprobe` skill 调用。\n服务地址：`http://webprobe.openclaw.svc:8000`（集群内部，外部不可直接访问）\n\n---\n\n## 技术栈\n\n| 组件 | 用途 |\n|---|---|\n| **FastAPI** | HTTP 服务框架，版本 WebProbe 0.2.0 |\n| **SearXNG** | 开源元搜索引擎，聚合 Google/Baidu/Bing 等，自部署无需 API Key |\n| **Crawl4AI** | 基于 Playwright 的 AI 爬虫库，内置正文提取、Markdown 转换、BM25 过滤 |\n| **Firecrawl** | 商业爬虫服务（当前未配置，应为备用方案） |\n\nhealth 接口确认：\n{\"status\":\"ok\",\"searxng\":true,\"crawl4ai\":true,\"firecrawl_configured\":false}\n\n---\n\n## API 接口（完整）\n\n### POST /search\n搜索网页，底层调 SearXNG。\n\n{\n \"query\": \"关键词\",\n \"lang\": \"zh-CN\",\n \"max_results\": 5, // 1-20\n \"engines\": [\"baidu\", \"google\"] // 可选，不传则全部引擎\n}\n\n### POST /scrape\n抓取单个页面，底层调 Crawl4AI（Playwright 渲染）。\n\n{\n \"url\": \"https://example.com\",\n \"max_length\": 20000, // 100-100000\n \"query\": \"关键词\", // 可选，传入则做 BM25 过滤\n \"extraction_schema\": {} // 可选，传入则做结构化提取\n}\n\nextraction_schema 示例：\n{\n \"name\": \"posts\",\n \"baseSelector\": \".athing\",\n \"fields\": [\n {\"name\": \"title\", \"selector\": \".titleline > a\", \"type\": \"text\"},\n {\"name\": \"url\", \"selector\": \".titleline > a\", \"type\": \"attribute\", \"attribute\": \"href\"}\n ]\n}\n\n### POST /extract\n抓取页面 + 强制 BM25 过滤，专门用于从长文中找特定信息。\n\n{\n \"url\": \"https://example.com\",\n \"query\": \"核心结论是什么\", // 必填\n \"max_length\": 20000 // 100-100000\n}\n\n### POST /deep-scrape\n从起始 URL 递归爬取多页。\n\n{\n \"url\": \"https://docs.example.com/\",\n \"max_pages\": 5, // 1-20\n \"max_depth\": 2, // 1-5\n \"strategy\": \"bfs\", // bfs 广度优先 或 dfs 深度优先\n \"query\": \"关键词\", // 可选，BM25 过滤\n \"url_pattern\": \"docs\\\\.example\\\\.com/guide/\", // 可选，URL 正则过滤\n \"max_length\": 10000 // 每页 100-50000\n}\n\n### GET /health\n{\"status\":\"ok\",\"searxng\":true,\"crawl4ai\":true,\"firecrawl_configured\":false}\n\n---\n\n## 架构图\n\nOpenClaw (skill)\n │\n │ HTTP POST\n ▼\nWebProbe 服务 (FastAPI 0.2.0)\n ├── /search ──→ SearXNG（元搜索，聚合多引擎）\n └── /scrape\n /extract ──→ Crawl4AI（Playwright 无头浏览器）\n /deep-scrape\n\n---\n\n## 自建参考\n\n### 核心依赖\npip install fastapi uvicorn crawl4ai rank_bm25 jieba\nplaywright install chromium --with-deps\n\n### SearXNG 部署\nservices:\n searxng:\n image: searxng/searxng\n ports: [\"8080:8080\"]\n volumes:\n - ./searxng:/etc/searxng\n\n### Crawl4AI 快速上手\nfrom crawl4ai import AsyncWebCrawler\n\nasync with AsyncWebCrawler() as crawler:\n result = await crawler.arun(url=\"https://example.com\")\n print(result.markdown)\n\n---\n\n## 参考链接\n\n- SearXNG：https://github.com/searxng/searxng\n- Crawl4AI：https://github.com/unclecode/crawl4ai\n- Firecrawl（商业备选）：https://github.com/mendableai/firecrawl"}],"timestamp":1775545529914}}
